data.title: College Readiness Workshops at WESM
data.meta_description:
The LMU Family of Schools (LMU FOS) is a university collaborative between Loyola Marymount University and thirteen fourteen schools in the Westchester community.  We focus on college and career readiness programs, school culture and climate issues, and student achievement.  

We would like to invite you to participate in the following programs to prepare you for college :
